<p>
  <span class="nym">Aldrich</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>alt</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon, Old Frisian</span> <i>ald</i> 'old' + <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>rih</i> 'ruler'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


